          "description": "The Mineral Springs Public Restrooms are a pleasant surprise in the heart of the city. Nestled near the park, they are incredibly easy to find and offer a clean, well-maintained space for visitors. The location is truly superb, making it a convenient stop for anyone exploring the area. While the men\u2019s room could use some updates to match the overall quality, the facilities are functional and serve their purpose well. It\u2019s a relief to find such a clean and accessible restroom in a bustling urban setting. Whether you're out for a stroll in the park or just passing through, these restrooms are a reliable spot to take a quick break.",
