          "description": "The location of this place is superb, men\u2019s room needs some significant repairs and upgrades to become a truly 5 star worthy restroom\n\nThe most important upgrade this men\u2019s restroom needs is improved ventilation, there is already an air shaft above the toilet stall but I\u2019m thinking that some kind of fan should be added to improve air flow, increase sanitation, and reduce odors\n\nThe staff here is usually quite ridiculous and thuggish, I\u2019ve been threatened on multiple occasions for attempting to have some conversations about proper public restroom management protocols\n\nEven the managers don\u2019t seem to be capable of any kind of above average restaurant or bathroom service, probably they have never even managed to earn the privilege of attending a high quality place to see how well things can possibly be done\n\nI\u2019ve made an extensive list of repairs and upgrades that I think need to be made, I will include screenshots:",
